          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/707.-step-4-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, roll the <strong>lemon<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> on a hard surface (to release more juice) then cut in half</p>\r\n<p>Mix together the <strong>mayonnaise</strong>, <strong>mint</strong>, juice from the <strong>lemon<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> and 2 tbsp<span class=\"text-danger\"> [4 tbsp]</span><strong> olive oil</strong> - this is your <strong>dressing</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/707.-step-5-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/707.-step-5-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
